            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For 1-2 channels and light posting, yes. Buffer free, Metricool free, and Publer free all cover the basics. The ceiling hits fast — most caps you at 10-30 scheduled posts. Once you cross 3 channels or want analytics, the paid tier becomes cheaper than your time.</p></div></div>
